WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.470
So the timeline I'm going to

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:05.030
tell you the detail of what the

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:07.990
Lord showed me when he came to

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.910
me as a massive, fiery light, and the

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:17.349
light was so bright. It literally

00:00:17.359 --> 00:00:19.590
felt like my spiritual eyes—my whole

00:00:19.590 --> 00:00:19.600
body—was

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.510
melting. I

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:23.670
literally said, "Lord, if you don't take

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:25.349
and dim the light down and do

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:26.870
something, I feel like it's going to

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:29.830
kill me, like it's going to burn me

00:00:29.830 --> 00:00:29.840
up."And

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.630
all of a sudden, because he knew

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:34.709
it, he was so intense. And I'm

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:36.709
telling you, in any intensity, I've

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:38.229
never seen anything like this before in

00:00:38.239 --> 00:00:41.670
my life. He took something and he

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:42.750
shielded

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:46.150
himself.

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:49.670
It was like a shield, and all of

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:52.790
the light that was shining upon my face

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:54.790
where it felt like it was

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:57.670
blinding me, it came

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:00.389
out the side of

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:03.310
the shield. The light was still

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:07.510
going, but it was being shaded and I

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:10.390
could see up in it. And all of a sudden,

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:14.310
a massive dove comes out of it with

00:01:14.310 --> 00:01:14.320
its

00:01:14.320 --> 00:01:16.789
wings flapping and an olive branch.

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:19.910
It came over the top of me

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:23.109
and the glory of the Lord filled me.

00:01:25.799 --> 00:01:28.070
And all of a sudden he said,

00:01:28.070 --> 00:01:28.080
"Brandon,

00:01:28.080 --> 00:01:32.069
I want to show you

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:37.429
the time frame of humanity from

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:40.390
the beginning of creation to where we

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.950
are right

00:01:41.950 --> 00:01:41.960
now."And

00:01:41.960 --> 00:01:45.190
he showed me a

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:48.069
thin line; it looked like a

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:50.630
thread that went through the spans of

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:53.109
humanity. It went from the beginning all

00:01:53.119 --> 00:01:54.310
the way to where we are.

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:56.230
He

00:01:56.240 --> 00:02:00.550
divided it by thousand-year increments. It

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.709
went 1,000 years, 2,000 years, 3,000

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:05.270
years, 4,000 years, 5,000 years, 6,000

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:08.070
years, and that's where we were.

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:11.350
And then he divided it again

00:02:11.350 --> 00:02:11.360
into

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:13.110
these little blocks. So you could

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.470
take a piece of paper and divide it

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:16.470
out into a thousand, and then he divided

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:19.270
in between those thousands by hundreds,

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.550
and then he divided it by

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:25.990
tens. So

00:02:25.990 --> 00:02:26.000
for

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:29.990
each year, I could see faces.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:33.550
But I just want to say

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:38.470
this: from the beginning of time, the

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:43.110
dead in Christ—all of the

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:45.790
believers that are in the

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:49.070
dirt—it

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:52.869
looked to me

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:54.390
like there were millions of

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:57.229
them. I could see their

00:02:57.239 --> 00:02:59.670
bones

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:05.750
in the first couple layers of soil

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:09.030
around the whole earth. There

00:03:09.030 --> 00:03:09.040
were

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:11.229
skulls,

00:03:11.239 --> 00:03:14.949
hands, and legs; the

00:03:14.959 --> 00:03:19.070
bones of the believers were still in the

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:20.910
dirt like

00:03:20.920 --> 00:03:23.830
fossilized remains. And they were looking in the

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:28.149
spirit realm up toward the Father. The

00:03:28.159 --> 00:03:30.630
bones were a representation. I

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:32.390
know "to be absent from the body is to be

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.670
present with the Lord,"that's what the

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:36.149
Bible says. But it was like they

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:39.110
were looking up in the spirit realm

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:42.350
waiting for the "dead in Christ will rise

00:03:42.350 --> 00:03:42.360
first."And

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:45.830
I could see the anticipation

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:47.070
in the

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:50.630
earth waiting for the Son of Man to come

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:53.110
at the rapture of the church, waiting for

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:55.990
the coming of the Lord.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:59.830
The ground was anticipating.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.949
The bones were anticipating, kind of like

00:04:02.959 --> 00:04:06.550
"Can these bones live?"like it

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:08.110
talks about in the

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:12.990
Bible. The bones were anticipating the

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:16.150
glory, and there was

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:19.789
an atmosphere of acceleration

00:04:19.789 --> 00:04:19.799
and

00:04:19.799 --> 00:04:22.870
excitement in the bones. I don't know

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:26.790
how; it's just what I saw. So he said, "I

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:28.390
want to—"and this was something I

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:29.749
did not want to skip. That was so

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:31.670
important for you all to hear this: the

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:33.909
dead in Christ are going to rise first

00:04:33.919 --> 00:04:35.430
and we are going to be all caught up

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:38.550
with him. Watch what is

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:41.430
about to happen, folks. I am

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:45.950
so excited about it. Jesus is

00:04:45.960 --> 00:04:48.870
coming! It's so exciting. People

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:51.990
have talked about this for generations

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.469
and we're right there. The Lord even

00:04:54.479 --> 00:04:56.230
told me, "Brandon, I told you

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:59.189
there will be a generation that will not

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:02.830
taste death and you are that

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:06.150
generation. You will be that generation

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:08.749
that does not taste

00:05:08.759 --> 00:05:10.270
death."Wow.

00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:13.830
That's you! You're still here. I

00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:15.270
believe there's a remnant of you. I know

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:16.469
there's probably some elderly people

00:05:16.479 --> 00:05:18.230
that'll probably go home, but I'm

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:21.670
telling you, there is a generation that

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:24.870
will not taste death. We will be

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:26.870
the ones that are caught up. Glory to

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:30.710
God! And we will see the soon

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:33.950
return of our King.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:37.189
So whenever he took me on the timeline

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:39.990
and he took me by year, it was like he

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:43.830
could fast forward it on a DVD player or

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:46.390
a VCR. I know people don't use

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:49.430
VCRs now, but like a recorder

00:05:49.430 --> 00:05:49.440
where

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:51.350
you could speed it up, and I could see

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:53.909
the years panning out,

00:05:53.909 --> 00:05:53.919
moving

00:05:53.919 --> 00:05:55.710
really

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:58.070
fast in front of my face like

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:00.629
building Legos. In each one, I

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:02.390
could see the faces of the people that

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:04.189
were ruling in that

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:07.670
time going back. But he starts

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:11.390
it out speaking the world into

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:14.790
existence. And whenever

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:18.150
he spoke the earth, I saw the earth come

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:21.990
right before me like a ball of clay.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:26.390
A massive brown ball of clay came right

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:28.629
in front of me whenever he spoke it into

00:06:28.639 --> 00:06:30.950
existence. And it was without form and

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:34.309
void, right?

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:35.909
And darkness was on the face of the

00:06:35.919 --> 00:06:38.629
deep. It all happened right in front of

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:41.590
my face. And he's allowing me to see it

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:44.070
in the timeline. And it's a ball of

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:48.469
clay. It was a massive brown and red

00:06:48.479 --> 00:06:51.430
ball of clay. And when he spoke to it,

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:55.710
it started to form. But there were no

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:59.469
continents. It was all

00:06:59.479 --> 00:07:04.870
one big landmass in one area.

00:07:04.880 --> 00:07:07.909
There wasn't like South America,

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:10.629
North America, Asia, and all this;

00:07:10.639 --> 00:07:13.510
it was just one big thing. And I

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:15.350
don't know how it all was divided,

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:17.990
whether it was Noah's flood or

00:07:17.990 --> 00:07:18.000
whatever—which

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.909
I believe was Noah's flood that

00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:23.029
caused all this land to be divided and

00:07:23.039 --> 00:07:26.029
to create different continents.

00:07:26.039 --> 00:07:28.950
But when it first started, it was

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:33.589
a garden—a massive garden area.

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:37.589
So then he takes me to the garden and I

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:42.150
see Adam and he is ripped. He is not a

00:07:42.150 --> 00:07:42.160
plump

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:44.950
looking dude like me. I'm

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:49.430
still working on it. He has muscles

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:52.150
and he has a black-looking beard and

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:56.309
he's olive-skinned. I

00:07:56.319 --> 00:07:59.990
only saw his backside with the glory

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:03.070
around him. He had no clothes on in the

00:08:03.080 --> 00:08:06.550
natural; he had a glory around him.

00:08:06.560 --> 00:08:10.950
But he had black

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:13.830
hair and it went into his beard,

00:08:13.840 --> 00:08:16.150
and his black beard

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:18.270
was perfect.

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:21.589
The way he

00:08:21.599 --> 00:08:23.350
looked was amazing. His arms were

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:27.070
ripped. He did not look

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:32.070
deteriorated like how we look worn down.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:34.389
A lot of people's bodies look worn down.

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:37.070
His body was not dead. There was no

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:40.709
death. So he had no death around him.

00:08:40.719 --> 00:08:44.630
His body was fit and he looked good.

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:47.470
Like seriously, there was no

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:50.389
decay

00:08:50.389 --> 00:08:50.399
until—and

00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:51.829
I'm looking at it now and

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:53.670
I've thought about it all these

00:08:53.670 --> 00:08:53.680
days—there

00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:55.389
was no decay on him. He was not

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:57.750
dying. That did not happen until after

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:00.230
they bit the fruit. He was in a body

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:04.150
that renewed itself and it was perfect.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:07.190
So he was there and he was

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:10.550
communicating to this big

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:10.560
lizard-like

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:14.150
looking dinosaur thing that was like a

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:17.670
Jurassic Park massive

00:09:17.670 --> 00:09:17.680
long-neck

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:21.310
looking dinosaur and he was

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:24.949
communicating to this dinosaur. I could

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:28.030
see him pointing his finger at this

00:09:28.040 --> 00:09:30.710
dinosaur and the dinosaur was looking

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:33.110
down and was understanding what he was

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.790
saying. Kind of like how we talk to our

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:38.070
dogs or our cats or whatever. He was

00:09:38.080 --> 00:09:41.750
communicating to this massive dinosaur

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:43.350
and it was looking down at him. And

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:44.310
people say, "Well, I didn't think

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:47.670
prehistoric ages were in the

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:49.190
earth at that time or whatever, and

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:51.509
dinosaurs and T-Rexes and all that

00:09:51.509 --> 00:09:51.519
stuff."Well,

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:54.710
this lizard thing

00:09:54.710 --> 00:09:54.720
was—and

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.870
I did not see any other dinosaurs. I

00:09:56.880 --> 00:10:00.070
just saw one thing—and that dinosaur was

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:03.350
bending down and he was eating grass

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:05.550
and leaves off the

00:10:05.560 --> 00:10:09.430
trees. But I noticed this: there was no

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:13.269
death in the garden of trees. The trees

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:16.110
were not deteriorating with old dead

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:19.110
limbs. The leaves were not turning any

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:21.430
kind of dead-looking colors. They were

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:26.069
all perfect. There was nothing dying

00:10:26.079 --> 00:10:29.790
at all in the garden. Everything was

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:32.710
amazing. The trees were not

00:10:32.710 --> 00:10:32.720
like

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:34.310
these little—we have trees

00:10:34.310 --> 00:10:34.320
where

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:36.710
we go, "Wow, those are big

00:10:36.710 --> 00:10:36.720
trees."No,

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:39.590
these trees that I saw in

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:41.750
the garden, you couldn't put your

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:44.150
arms around them. They were ginormous

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:47.670
trees, and they were huge. They went

00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:50.389
so high up. They were not like the little

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:51.990
trees that we see now;

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:53.509
if

00:10:53.519 --> 00:10:55.910
they're 50 stories high, they're massive.

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:02.230
A redwood is

00:11:02.230 --> 00:11:02.240
huge—that's

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:03.990
the biggest tree

00:11:03.990 --> 00:11:04.000
we know—but

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:07.910
these trees were so huge,

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:10.550
and there was no death in them. All

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:12.710
the grass and the foliage was just

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:15.030
beautiful. But this is what I noticed

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:17.030
the most in this part of the vision that

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:21.230
the Lord allowed me to see: the sky was

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:25.030
alive. The atmosphere of the earth was alive,

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:28.870
and

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:32.190
it had a vibration to

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:35.670
it; it was vibrating.

00:11:35.670 --> 00:11:35.680
I

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:38.870
could feel it

00:11:38.880 --> 00:11:41.430
in the spirit when I was looking into it.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:43.829
What the Lord allowed me to feel was the

00:11:43.839 --> 00:11:47.110
energy, the vibration of the atmosphere

00:11:47.120 --> 00:11:49.150
above the Earth's

00:11:49.160 --> 00:11:52.069
canopy. It wasn't blue like it is

00:11:52.079 --> 00:11:56.670
right now; it was like our

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:59.750
sunsets where you see pinks and oranges

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:01.910
and all kinds of things. That's the way

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:05.750
the canopy looked. It had a life to

00:12:05.760 --> 00:12:08.069
it; it was almost like

00:12:08.079 --> 00:12:11.829
a fog, but it wasn't

00:12:11.839 --> 00:12:15.590
a fog. It was like thick water.

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:17.509
I don't know how else to say

00:12:17.519 --> 00:12:20.430
this, folks; it looked like

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:23.550
water above the

00:12:23.560 --> 00:12:26.470
atmosphere. It was all

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:28.629
beautiful. It was

00:12:28.629 --> 00:12:28.639
thick-looking,

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:30.949
almost like

00:12:30.959 --> 00:12:35.069
a transparent,

00:12:35.079 --> 00:12:39.670
translucent atmosphere. It

00:12:39.670 --> 00:12:39.680
was

00:12:39.680 --> 00:12:41.350
like a slime, but I

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:43.269
don't know how to say it because

00:12:43.279 --> 00:12:45.190
there was no structure to

00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:48.870
it; it wasn't a solid, but it

00:12:50.639 --> 00:12:52.389
was thick,

00:12:52.389 --> 00:12:52.399
like

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:55.910
moisture. There

00:12:55.910 --> 00:12:55.920
is

00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:58.069
no way to describe it with words.

00:12:58.079 --> 00:13:00.310
You could see the

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:02.629
stars through it. I could see lights

00:13:02.639 --> 00:13:05.430
through it, and you could see

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:07.509
pinks and purples. It was beautiful. It

00:13:07.509 --> 00:13:07.519
was

00:13:07.519 --> 00:13:09.430
like the sun was shining off of it,

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:12.230
making it alive and moving.

00:13:12.240 --> 00:13:15.350
Then I could see the

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:18.550
birds, and these were birds that

00:13:18.550 --> 00:13:18.560
are

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:20.550
not here anymore. There were

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:24.190
different kinds of birds with massive

00:13:24.200 --> 00:13:27.910
wingspans flying around in the

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:31.550
atmosphere in the garden. It was

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:34.150
beautiful. The water that the dinosaur was drinking was clear and

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:37.030
crystal,

00:13:37.040 --> 00:13:39.870
and there was no pollution.

00:13:48.519 --> 00:13:51.430
Then he takes me to another span of

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:52.790
time. He said, "I'm going

